<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="de">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Rentenkonzept – {{clientName}}</title>
    <style>
      * {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      body {
        font-family: 'Inter', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
        background: radial-gradient(circle at top left, #1b3d8b 0%, #0a1024 55%, #050610 100%);
        color: #f5f7ff;
        line-height: 1.5;
        -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;
        print-color-adjust: exact;
      }

      .layout {
        max-width: 1024px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 48px 40px 60px;
      }

      h1, h2, h3 {
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #ffffff;
      }

      p {
        color: #d1dcff;
      }

      .hero {
        position: relative;
        border-radius: 32px;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(20, 46, 115, 0.95), rgba(11, 24, 67, 0.92));
        padding: 48px;
        overflow: hidden;
        margin-bottom: 42px;
      }

      .hero::after {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        inset: 0;
        background: radial-gradient(circle at 20% -10%, rgba(80, 150, 255, 0.35), transparent 55%),
          radial-gradient(circle at 85% 25%, rgba(99, 233, 255, 0.15), transparent 60%),
          radial-gradient(circle at 50% 110%, rgba(103, 232, 249, 0.1), transparent 60%);
        pointer-events: none;
      }

      .hero-content {
        position: relative;
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
        gap: 32px;
        align-items: start;
      }

      .hero h1 {
        font-size: 36px;
        letter-spacing: -0.02em;
        margin-bottom: 16px;
      }

      .hero p.subtitle {
        font-size: 17px;
        max-width: 480px;
        color: #c2d5ff;
      }

      .meta-tags {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: 10px;
        margin-top: 20px;
      }

      .meta-tags span {
        padding: 8px 16px;
        border-radius: 999px;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
        font-size: 12px;
        font-weight: 500;
        letter-spacing: 0.05em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: #f5f7ff;
      }

      .cta-row {
        margin-top: 28px;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 18px;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
      }

      .cta-row .button {
        padding: 12px 28px;
        border-radius: 999px;
        background: #ffffff;
        color: #101827;
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: 14px;
        letter-spacing: 0.02em;
        border: none;
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 10px;
        box-shadow: 0 18px 45px rgba(11, 24, 67, 0.35);
      }

      .cta-meta {
        font-size: 13px;
        color: rgba(243, 246, 255, 0.65);
      }

      .preview-card {
        position: relative;
        border-radius: 28px;
        padding: 32px;
        background: linear-gradient(150deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.12), rgba(141,176,255,0.10));
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.18);
        box-shadow: 0 25px 60px rgba(5, 12, 40, 0.45);
      }

      .preview-card h3 {
        font-size: 18px;
        margin-bottom: 18px;
      }

      .progress-bar {
        margin: 20px 0 28px;
      }

      .progress-label {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: rgba(215, 226, 255, 0.8);
        margin-bottom: 8px;
      }

      .progress-track {
        height: 12px;
        border-radius: 999px;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
        overflow: hidden;
      }

      .progress-fill {
        height: 100%;
        border-radius: 999px;
        background: linear-gradient(90deg, #4ade80 0%, #22d3ee 55%, #818cf8 100%);
      }

      .preview-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
        gap: 16px;
      }

      .preview-item {
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
        border-radius: 20px;
        padding: 14px 18px;
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
      }

      .preview-item p.label {
        font-size: 12px;
        letter-spacing: 0.04em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: rgba(210, 224, 255, 0.7);
        margin-bottom: 6px;
      }

      .preview-item p.value {
        font-size: 18px;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #ffffff;
      }

      .cards-grid {
        margin-top: 32px;
        display: grid;
        gap: 24px;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
      }

      .glass-card {
        border-radius: 26px;
        padding: 28px;
        background: rgba(14, 25, 58, 0.65);
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
        box-shadow: 0 26px 50px rgba(5, 9, 30, 0.35);
      }

      .glass-card.light {
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
      }

      .glass-card h2 {
        font-size: 20px;
        margin-bottom: 18px;
      }

      .stat-row {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: baseline;
        font-size: 14px;
        color: rgba(215, 226, 255, 0.8);
        margin: 10px 0;
      }

      .stat-row strong {
        color: #ffffff;
        font-size: 18px;
        font-weight: 600;
      }

      .divider {
        height: 1px;
        background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,255,255,0), rgba(255,255,255,0.18), rgba(255,255,255,0));
        margin: 18px 0;
      }

      .badge {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        padding: 6px 14px;
        border-radius: 999px;
        font-size: 11px;
        font-weight: 600;
        letter-spacing: 0.08em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
      }

      .badge.success {
        background: rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.18);
        color: #bbf7d0;
        border: 1px solid rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.3);
      }

      .badge.warning {
        background: rgba(252, 165, 54, 0.18);
        color: #fde68a;
        border: 1px solid rgba(251, 191, 36, 0.3);
      }

      .metrics-grid {
        margin-top: 42px;
        display: grid;
        gap: 18px;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
      }

      .metric-box {
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 20px;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        min-height: 120px;
      }

      .metric-box p.label {
        font-size: 12px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.06em;
        color: rgba(216, 226, 255, 0.6);
        margin-bottom: 10px;
      }

      .metric-box p.value {
        font-size: 22px;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #ffffff;
      }

      .scenario-section {
        margin-top: 48px;
      }

      .scenario-header {
        display: flex;
        align-items: baseline;
        justify-content: space-between;
        margin-bottom: 18px;
      }

      .scenario-header h2 {
        font-size: 24px;
      }

      .scenario-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr));
        gap: 24px;
      }

      .scenario-card {
        border-radius: 24px;
        padding: 26px;
        background: rgba(12, 22, 50, 0.82);
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
        box-shadow: 0 22px 50px rgba(7, 15, 35, 0.35);
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 18px;
      }

      .scenario-card.variant-current {
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
      }

      .scenario-card.variant-optimized {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.16), rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.22));
        border: 1px solid rgba(129, 140, 248, 0.35);
      }

      .scenario-card h3 {
        font-size: 18px;
      }

      .scenario-badge {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 8px;
        padding: 6px 14px;
        border-radius: 999px;
        font-size: 11px;
        letter-spacing: 0.08em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: rgba(226, 232, 255, 0.85);
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.18);
      }

      .scenario-card.variant-optimized .scenario-badge {
        background: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.18);
        border-color: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.36);
        color: #bbf7d0;
      }

      .scenario-stats {
        display: grid;
        gap: 10px;
        font-size: 13px;
        color: rgba(218, 228, 255, 0.75);
      }

      .scenario-stats strong {
        font-size: 20px;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #ffffff;
      }

      .scenario-progress {
        margin-top: 4px;
      }

      .scenario-progress-bar {
        height: 8px;
        border-radius: 999px;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
        overflow: hidden;
      }

      .scenario-progress-fill {
        height: 100%;
        background: linear-gradient(90deg, #22d3ee 0%, #38bdf8 50%, #6366f1 100%);
        border-radius: 999px;
      }

      .scenario-highlight {
        font-size: 12px;
        color: rgba(226, 232, 255, 0.7);
      }

      .analysis-section {
        margin-top: 48px;
        border-radius: 28px;
        background: rgba(3, 9, 28, 0.85);
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
        padding: 36px;
      }

      .analysis-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr));
        gap: 24px;
      }

      .analysis-card {
        background: rgba(11, 24, 67, 0.65);
        border-radius: 20px;
        padding: 20px 22px;
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
      }

      .analysis-card h3 {
        font-size: 16px;
        margin-bottom: 12px;
      }

      .analysis-card p {
        color: rgba(215, 226, 255, 0.85);
        font-size: 14px;
      }

      .attachments {
        margin-top: 30px;
      }

      .attachments h4 {
        margin-bottom: 14px;
        font-size: 15px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.12em;
        color: rgba(203, 213, 255, 0.9);
      }

      .attachment-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
        gap: 18px;
      }

      .attachment-card {
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
        border-radius: 18px;
        padding: 14px;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 12px;
      }

      .attachment-card img {
        width: 100%;
        border-radius: 12px;
        object-fit: cover;
      }

      .attachment-card span {
        font-size: 12px;
        color: rgba(219, 226, 255, 0.75);
      }

      .footer-note {
        margin-top: 48px;
        font-size: 12px;
        line-height: 1.5;
        color: rgba(168, 189, 255, 0.6);
        text-align: center;
      }

      @media print {
        body {
          background: #050610;
        }
        .hero,
        .preview-card,
        .glass-card,
        .analysis-card,
        .metric-box,
        .analysis-section,
        .attachment-card {
          box-shadow: none !important;
        }
        .layout {
          padding: 32px 30px 40px;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <main class="layout">
      <header class="hero">
        <div class="hero-content">
          <div>
            <p class="subtitle" style="text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.28em; font-size: 13px; color: rgba(212, 223, 255, 0.75); margin-bottom: 16px;">
              Finance Made Simple · Individuelles Rentenkonzept
            </p>
            <h1>Rentenlücke verstehen – und smart schließen.</h1>
            <p class="subtitle">
              Klar, modern, messbar: Dieses Dashboard fasst deine aktuelle Versorgungssituation zusammen,
              zeigt Optimierungspotenziale und liefert belastbare Kennzahlen für die Entscheidung.
            </p>
            <div class="meta-tags">
              <span>DSGVO-konform</span>
              <span>Berater-ready</span>
              <span>PDF-Export</span>
              <span>Stripe/SevDesk-fähig</span>
            </div>
            <div class="cta-row">
              <div class="button">Detailanalyse geöffnet</div>
              <div class="cta-meta">
                Erstellung: {{generatedAtIso}}<br />
                Kunde: {{clientName}}
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="preview-card">
            <h3>Quick Preview – Deckungsgrad deiner Zielrente</h3>
            <div class="progress-bar">
              <div class="progress-label">
                <span>Aktueller Deckungsgrad</span>
                <span><strong>{{gapCoveragePercent}}%</strong> von {{targetPensionNetto}} €</span>
              </div>
              <div class="progress-track">
                <div class="progress-fill" style="width: {{gapCoveragePercentRaw}}%;"></div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="preview-grid">
              <div class="preview-item">
                <p class="label">Bisher gedeckt (netto)</p>
                <p class="value">
                  {{#if statutoryNetCurrent}}{{statutoryNetCurrent}}{{else}}0,00{{/if}} €
                  {{#if privateNetCurrentRaw}}
                    + {{privateNetCurrent}} €
                  {{/if}}
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="preview-item">
                <p class="label">Wunschziel (netto)</p>
                <p class="value">{{#if targetPensionNetto}}{{targetPensionNetto}}{{else}}–{{/if}} €</p>
              </div>
              <div class="preview-item">
                <p class="label">Aktuelle Versorgungslücke</p>
                <p class="value" style="color:#fca5a5;">{{#if gapBefore}}{{gapBefore}}{{else}}0,00{{/if}} €</p>
              </div>
              <div class="preview-item">
                <p class="label">Netto-Ziel nach Optimierung</p>
                <p class="value">{{#if plannedNetFuture}}{{plannedNetFuture}}{{else}}–{{/if}} €</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </header>

      <section class="cards-grid">
        <article class="glass-card">
          <div class="badge warning">Ist-Situation</div>
          <h2>Deine aktuelle Rentenlücke</h2>
          <p style="margin-bottom: 14px; color: rgba(215, 226, 255, 0.8);">
            Auf Basis deiner Angaben ergibt sich aktuell folgende Netto-Situation:
          </p>
          <div class="stat-row">
            <span>Gesetzliche Rente (netto)</span>
            <strong>{{#if statutoryNetCurrent}}{{statutoryNetCurrent}}{{else}}–{{/if}} €</strong>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-row">
            <span>Private Vorsorge (netto)</span>
            <strong>{{#if privateNetCurrent}}{{privateNetCurrent}}{{else}}–{{/if}} €</strong>
          </div>
          <div class="divider"></div>
          <div class="stat-row" style="font-size: 16px;">
            <span>Versorgungslücke (monatl.)</span>
            <strong style="color: #fca5a5;">{{#if gapBefore}}{{gapBefore}}{{else}}–{{/if}} €</strong>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="glass-card light">
          <div class="badge success">Empfehlung</div>
          <h2>Optimierung durch neue Sparrate</h2>
          <p style="margin-bottom: 14px; color: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.75);">
            Die geplante Sparrate erzeugt folgende zusätzliche Netto-Rente:
          </p>
          <div class="stat-row" style="color: rgba(15,23,42,0.75);">
            <span>Zusatzeinnahmen (netto)</span>
            <strong style="color:#0f172a;">{{#if plannedNetFuture}}{{plannedNetFuture}}{{else}}–{{/if}} €</strong>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-row" style="color: rgba(15,23,42,0.75);">
            <span>Zusatzeinnahmen (brutto)</span>
            <strong style="color:#0f172a;">{{#if plannedGrossFuture}}{{plannedGrossFuture}}{{else}}–{{/if}} €</strong>
          </div>
          <div class="divider" style="background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(15,23,42,0), rgba(15,23,42,0.2), rgba(15,23,42,0));"></div>
          <div class="stat-row" style="font-size: 16px; color: rgba(15,23,42,0.75);">
            <span>Restlücke nach Umsetzung</span>
            <strong style="color: {{#if gapAfterRaw}}#f97316{{else}}#16a34a{{/if}};">
              {{#if gapAfter}}{{gapAfter}}{{else}}0,00{{/if}} €
            </strong>
          </div>
          <p style="margin-top: 8px; font-size: 13px; color: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.65);">
            Monatliche Sparrate erforderlich: <strong>{{#if requiredSavingsMonthly}}{{requiredSavingsMonthly}}{{else}}–{{/if}} €</strong>
          </p>
        </article>
      </section>

      <section class="metrics-grid">
        <div class="metric-box">
          <p class="label">Deckungsgrad</p>
          <p class="value">{{#if gapCoveragePercent}}{{gapCoveragePercent}}{{else}}0,0{{/if}} %</p>
          <p style="font-size:12px; color: rgba(216,226,255,0.6); margin-top: 6px;">Abgedeckter Anteil der Zielrente</p>
        </div>
        <div class="metric-box">
          <p class="label">Empfohlene Sparrate</p>
          <p class="value">{{#if requiredSavingsMonthly}}{{requiredSavingsMonthly}}{{else}}–{{/if}} €</p>
          <p style="font-size:12px; color: rgba(216,226,255,0.6); margin-top: 6px;">monatlich erforderlich</p>
        </div>
        <div class="metric-box">
          <p class="label">Zusatzeinnahmen geplant</p>
          <p class="value">{{#if plannedNetFuture}}{{plannedNetFuture}}{{else}}–{{/if}} €</p>
          <p style="font-size:12px; color: rgba(216,226,255,0.6); margin-top: 6px;">zusätzliche Netto-Rente</p>
        </div>
        <div class="metric-box">
          <p class="label">Empfohlene Netto-Rente</p>
          <p class="value">{{#if requiredSavingsNetFuture}}{{requiredSavingsNetFuture}}{{else}}–{{/if}} €</p>
          <p style="font-size:12px; color: rgba(216,226,255,0.6); margin-top: 6px;">Netto bei Zielerreichung</p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="scenario-section">
        <div class="scenario-header">
          <h2>Deine Szenarien im direkten Vergleich</h2>
          <p style="font-size:13px; color: rgba(203, 213, 255, 0.65);">
            Zielrente: {{#if targetPensionNetto}}{{targetPensionNetto}}{{else}}–{{/if}} € (netto)
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="scenario-grid">
          <article class="scenario-card">
            <div class="scenario-badge">Ohne private Vorsorge</div>
            <h3>Nur gesetzliche Versorgung</h3>
            <div class="scenario-stats">
              <div>
                Aktuelle Rente (netto)<br />
                <strong>{{#if scenarioBaseNet}}{{scenarioBaseNet}}{{else}}–{{/if}} €</strong>
              </div>
              <div>
                Monatliche Lücke<br />
                <strong style="color:#fca5a5;">{{#if scenarioBaseGap}}{{scenarioBaseGap}}{{else}}–{{/if}} €</strong>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="scenario-highlight">
              Ohne private Ergänzung fehlen monatlich {{#if scenarioBaseGap}}{{scenarioBaseGap}}{{else}}–{{/if}} € zum Ziel.
            </p>
          </article>

          <article class="scenario-card variant-current">
            <div class="scenario-badge">Mit bestehender Vorsorge</div>
            <h3>Ist-Stand inklusive privater Vorsorge</h3>
            <div class="scenario-stats">
              <div>
                Gesamtrente (netto)<br />
                <strong>{{#if scenarioCurrentNet}}{{scenarioCurrentNet}}{{else}}–{{/if}} €</strong>
              </div>
              <div>
                Restlücke<br />
                <strong style="color:#fb923c;">{{#if scenarioCurrentGap}}{{scenarioCurrentGap}}{{else}}–{{/if}} €</strong>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="scenario-highlight">
              Die bestehende Vorsorge reduziert die Lücke, deckt sie aber noch nicht vollständig.
            </p>
          </article>

          <article class="scenario-card variant-optimized">
            <div class="scenario-badge">Empfohlen</div>
            <h3>Mit geplanter Sparrate</h3>
            <div class="scenario-stats">
              <div>
                Gesamtrente (netto)<br />
                <strong>{{#if scenarioOptimizedNet}}{{scenarioOptimizedNet}}{{else}}–{{/if}} €</strong>
              </div>
              <div>
                Restlücke<br />
                <strong style="color:#bbf7d0;">{{#if scenarioOptimizedGap}}{{scenarioOptimizedGap}}{{else}}0,00{{/if}} €</strong>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="scenario-progress">
              <div class="scenario-progress-bar">
                <div class="scenario-progress-fill" style="width: {{#if scenarioOptimizedCoverageRaw}}{{scenarioOptimizedCoverageRaw}}{{else}}0{{/if}}%;"></div>
              </div>
              <p class="scenario-highlight" style="margin-top: 8px;">
                Deckungsgrad: {{#if scenarioOptimizedCoverage}}{{scenarioOptimizedCoverage}}{{else}}0,0{{/if}} %
              </p>
            </div>
          </article>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="analysis-section">
        <h2 style="font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 24px;">Analyse &amp; Narrative</h2>
        <div class="analysis-grid">
          <div class="analysis-card">
            <h3>Gesetzliche Versorgung</h3>
            {{#if statutoryStrengths}}
              <p><strong>Stärken:</strong> {{statutoryStrengths}}</p>
            {{else}}
              <p style="color: rgba(215, 226, 255, 0.6);">Keine Stärken hinterlegt.</p>
            {{/if}}
            <div class="divider"></div>
            {{#if statutoryWeaknesses}}
              <p><strong>Schwächen:</strong> {{statutoryWeaknesses}}</p>
            {{else}}
              <p style="color: rgba(215, 226, 255, 0.6);">Keine Schwächen hinterlegt.</p>
            {{/if}}
          </div>
          <div class="analysis-card">
            <h3>Private Vorsorge</h3>
            {{#if privateStrengths}}
              <p><strong>Stärken:</strong> {{privateStrengths}}</p>
            {{else}}
              <p style="color: rgba(215, 226, 255, 0.6);">Keine Stärken hinterlegt.</p>
            {{/if}}
            <div class="divider"></div>
            {{#if privateWeaknesses}}
              <p><strong>Schwächen:</strong> {{privateWeaknesses}}</p>
            {{else}}
              <p style="color: rgba(215, 226, 255, 0.6);">Keine Schwächen hinterlegt.</p>
            {{/if}}
          </div>
          <div class="analysis-card">
            <h3>Empfehlung &amp; Story</h3>
            {{#if recommendation}}
              <p>{{recommendation}}</p>
            {{else}}
              <p style="color: rgba(215, 226, 255, 0.6);">Noch keine individuelle Empfehlung hinterlegt.</p>
            {{/if}}
            {{#if recommendationDelta}}
              <div class="divider"></div>
              <p><strong>Zusatzeffekt:</strong> {{recommendationDelta}} € monatliche Mehrleistung</p>
            {{/if}}
          </div>
        </div>

        {{#if statutoryAttachments.length}}
          <div class="attachments">
            <h4>Analyse-Unterlagen gesetzliche Versorgung</h4>
            <div class="attachment-grid">
              {{#each statutoryAttachments}}
                <div class="attachment-card">
                  <img src="{{fileUrl}}" alt="{{originalName}}" />
                  <span>{{originalName}}</span>
                </div>
              {{/each}}
            </div>
          </div>
        {{/if}}

        {{#if privateAttachments.length}}
          <div class="attachments" style="margin-top: 22px;">
            <h4>Analyse-Unterlagen private Vorsorge</h4>
            <div class="attachment-grid">
              {{#each privateAttachments}}
                <div class="attachment-card">
                  <img src="{{fileUrl}}" alt="{{originalName}}" />
                  <span>{{originalName}}</span>
                </div>
              {{/each}}
            </div>
          </div>
        {{/if}}
      </section>

      <p class="footer-note">
        Hinweis: Die dargestellten Werte sind modellhafte Berechnungen und ersetzen keine individuelle Steuer- oder Rechtsberatung.
        Gesetzliche Änderungen sowie persönliche Lebensumstände können zu Abweichungen führen.
      </p>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>



